Roman has no proprietary period.

00:57:53.520 --> 00:57:57.880
The data will all be public immediately and we'll be serving data in the cloud and on

00:57:57.880 --> 00:57:58.120
front.

00:57:58.120 --> 00:57:58.480
Wow.

